                                and start closing more deals."
                            </p>
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                <div
                                    class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-accent/20 border border-accent/20"
                                >
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="text-sm font-bold">
                                        Jason Schell
                                    </p>
                                    <p class="text-xs text-blue-200">
                                        Owner, Human Led AI
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-16 text-center text-text-muted/60 text-sm">
                ¬© 2025 Human Led AI. All rights reserved.
